text: Guo Ning (born 23 January 1995) is a Chinese water polo player. She played at the 2017 World Aquatics Championships, 2018 Asian Games, and 2019 World Aquatics Championships. == References == == Other websites == * Guo Ning of China #6 throws during the Women's Water Polo Qualification match Getty Category:1995 births Category:Chinese water polo players Category:Living people
